Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.19,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我记忆中这里的冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.13,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像没有这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:25.63,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从东京回到山形老家快两个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:29.52,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这期间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.59,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我度过了忐忑不安的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.54,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:53.09,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:06.71,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位的哀伤我们感同身受 请节哀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:10.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在行纳棺仪式前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请允许我向往生者上一柱香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.84,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托了 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:46.97,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看上去还像活着似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.24,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是烧炭自杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:52.50,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,表情很安详
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:59.59,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死在冰冷的车里发现得早就会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:04.74,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.74,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:15.64,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:23.05,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在让我们祝福往生者能够安详平和地离去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.67,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请允许我为她举行纳棺仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请在场的各位亲属也共同参与
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:32.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来请允许我擦拭身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:09.92,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.27,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有一个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:13.38,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.79,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.57,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有点事想问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.93,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:09.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一会儿换完衣服要开始给往生者化妆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:14.05,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有男性化妆和女性化妆的区别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:16.96,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 请稍等一下 好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.86,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐 想给留男妆扮成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:24.38,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是男孩啊 还是女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:28.27,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:32.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是我当初把他生成一个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.91,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就不会有今天这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:38.96,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.80,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那化女孩吧 女妆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:45.87,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.46,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,化女孩 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:49.45,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.50,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留男
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:22.58,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,入 殓 师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.24,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天的观众也不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.99,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们应该在宣传上再下点功夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:24.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.78,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做个乐团的网页
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:29.54,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我老婆是平面设计师 可以让她免费设计一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:32.71,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,省省吧 大悟君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.23,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还撑得住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:35.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:36.79,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:37.68,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非逞强买好琴 还不赶紧找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 今天辛苦大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.53,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:52.74,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上座率虽然不是很高 大家仍然保持了很高的演奏水平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃 情况是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:04.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天我们乐团的老板曾根崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有几句话想对在坐的各位同仁说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.92,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请大家集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:27.62,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乐团解散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.25,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.94,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好不容易才抓住的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:47.06,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样一瞬间成为了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大提琴没有任何过错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:58.61,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是不走运被我这种人买来 我失业了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从哪方面讲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:05.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这把琴对于我都太奢侈了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.96,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 谢谢您了  - 很新鲜 马上吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:18.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我回来了 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.41,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,章鱼 邻居送的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:23.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恰好在门口遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.25,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说是早上刚钓上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:33.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:37.58,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:39.92,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乐团
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.02,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.48,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就自己找下一家就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.97,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有下家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.80,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我这种水平很难找到活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:07.77,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还要还贷款
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.52,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:24.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放心好了 一百万嘛 靠我的平面设计 还是没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.44,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一千八百万
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一千八百万
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:33.39,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,专业的都用这种价钱的 这把算便宜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么瞒着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:43.41,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想你一定会反对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:50.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么重要的事怎么不跟我商量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.78,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.43,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去做饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,世界上任何地方都是我们的新居
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:20.38,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,周游世界 来个演奏之旅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:24.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我的求婚誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:28.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可现实太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:34.59,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不对 是我应该更早地承认自己根本没有那个才能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:42.86,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.39,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.90,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快 大悟 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.05,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别再被抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.46,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:42.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 什么呀  - 大提琴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.16,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放弃了做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:53.35,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回乡下的山形老家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.24,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:11.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为是妈妈留给你的房子啊 不需要付房租
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:14.03,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是把好琴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.63,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本以为这是我人生的重要决择
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:32.07,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到卖了琴 反而轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:38.96,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直被它束缚着 现在终于解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:46.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直追逐的梦想 也许从来就不曾存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:05.19,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,母亲两年前去世了 这是她留给我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:10.29,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父亲曾在这经营过咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我几乎记不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:20.02,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他有了外遇 跟别的女人走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:23.46,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,母亲把这里改成一家小酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:27.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并靠它把我抚养成人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:31.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大悟 晚饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:34.29,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:44.52,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还以为你会讨厌乡下的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.41,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感觉很新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.62,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概水的关系 米饭变得很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.44,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许 我该在这儿开家店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.07,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:09.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个 这个 年龄不限 待遇从优
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:13.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且实际工作时间很短 正式员工
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:17.09,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,NK代理 什么公司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:21.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与送行有关的工作 是旅行社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做导游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:29.00,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这儿写着不需要工作经验 总之先打个电话问问看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:54.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.86,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,NK代理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:11.66,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 这里是NK代理吗  - 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:15.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是小林 早晨打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:20.48,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是来面试的 社长马上回来 你坐这等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.41,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:40.24,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本来我是反对社长在报纸上打广告的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干我们这一行 招人特别难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:49.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问 这儿是做什么生意的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:53.29,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么 你什么都不知道就过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.64,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,报上说是协助旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:03.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不...不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:14.86,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 社长 来应聘的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:18.38,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,初次见面 我是早晨打过电话的小林
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.43,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比电话里阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:28.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看 广告登对了吧 倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我把简历带过来了  - 哦 好 请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:37.50,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:50.11,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 能做全职吗  - 啊 我...我 哎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.44,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你叫什么来着  - 小林大悟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.88,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 给他印盒名片  - 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:02.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请 请等一下 您还没谈工资和其它待遇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:06.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 对了 开始一巴掌行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.75,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一巴掌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:13.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 五万元是吗?  - 五十
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,五十万
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:19.39,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嫌少？ -不不不 能拿到那么多工资
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.24,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不相信每天付现金也行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:24.18,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是 请...请...请问我做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:27.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:32.47,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始 先做我的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.57,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,具体做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:36.96,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,具体的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:40.69,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 纳棺  - 纳棺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把遗体放进棺木
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:46.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开花了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:50.65,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遗体是指死去的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的问题很幼稚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:05.44,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 广告上好像是说协助旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:08.87,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我以为是旅行社的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:11.78,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 哦 那个印错了  - 错了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:15.19,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是协助旅行 准确地说是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安心地走上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:21.09,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.81,0:22:25.79,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为 NK是纳棺的缩写
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.75,0:22:30.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 也是我们有缘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.29,0:22:35.23,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先试试看吧 干不了再辞也来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:39.80,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 今天的工资  - 啊...不不不 不能要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:42.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 没关系 拿去吧  - 不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:04.65,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:07.43,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.81,0:23:09.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 给  - 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:12.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是说过搬过来要吃牛肉火锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:15.68,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,米泽牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:19.73,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 上等的里脊  - 太好了 一定很贵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:22.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我预支的工资
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:25.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 哎 工作定下来啦  - 嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:27.90,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的 那算是庆祝喽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:33.43,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 到底做什么工作啊 是导游吗  - 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:36.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,销售员
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:40.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.38,0:23:44.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是什么旅行社
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:49.62,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 那是什么  - 和仪式有关的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.58,0:23:52.24,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,婚庆代理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.85,0:23:56.99,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是让你演奏大提琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:01.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我马上准备牛肉火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:02.90,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.36,0:24:05.23,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.41,0:24:20.53,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会太晚回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.27,0:24:25.67,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 路上小心  - 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.81,0:24:54.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.64,0:24:56.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请您多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.39,0:24:59.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新桌子送来前 先用社长的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.88,0:25:09.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,名片印好啦 这回没印错
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.53,0:25:31.92,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前从没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.11,0:25:34.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 还真是第一次见  - 第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.19,0:25:39.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祖父在我不懂事的时候就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.37,0:25:43.34,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,母亲去世时 我当时正好在国外 回来时已经安葬了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.85,0:25:47.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你父亲呢  - 我六岁时他同其他女人私奔了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.13,0:25:54.93,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么说 你母亲一定很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.32,0:26:12.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个从没见过尸体的人 能胜任这份工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.84,0:26:14.35,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间一长就习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.65,0:26:19.03,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,习惯...尸体?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.53,0:26:19.93,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.44,0:26:24.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在是夏天 所以没那么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.73,0:26:27.35,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等到了旺季 就会
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.67,0:26:29.87,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.03,0:26:32.76,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有很多活找上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.92,0:26:35.11,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 活都从哪来啊  - 殡葬公司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.37,0:26:39.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 殡葬啊  - 对
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.68,0:26:43.46,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纳棺的活 过去都是由死者家属做的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.91,0:26:46.16,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来才交给了殡葬公司
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.63,0:26:50.27,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于是呢 就有了我们现在这个行业
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.90,0:26:54.45,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以说是 夹缝中求生存的产业
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.69,0:26:56.58,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个还真重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.89,0:27:00.79,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,棺木有很多种
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.03,0:27:03.68,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,五万 十万 三十万
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.05,0:27:05.34,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相差这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.54,0:27:10.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个是三合板的 这个呢镶了金边 两侧还有木雕
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.64,0:27:14.50,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最贵的是这个 一整块桧木
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.92,0:27:17.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 用料和装饰决定价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.20,0:27:21.74,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 火化时就一样了 最终都变成了灰
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.02,0:27:25.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人这辈子最后买的东西 是由别人帮你挑选的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.62,0:27:27.13,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还真是讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.35,0:27:33.86,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好 这里是NK代理
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.68,0:27:37.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 他在
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.67,0:27:42.94,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是港座吗 马上 好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.97,0:27:47.01,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,社长打来的 来活了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.69,0:27:51.05,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来活...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.52,0:28:37.87,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- NK的人么？  - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.24,0:28:40.09,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.26,0:28:41.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.67,0:28:49.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是新来的 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.39,0:28:51.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小林 小林君
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.88,0:28:55.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是今天的模特 请多关照 模特
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.79,0:29:02.18,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小林君 换好了衣服\N我们就马上开始啦 请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.42,0:29:05.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小林君 来这边 来吧 化妆 换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.66,0:29:07.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,化妆
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.26,0:29:08.09,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.03,0:29:11.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.26,0:29:14.33,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事 没事 拜托了 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.39,0:29:23.05,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纳棺仪式 首选用棉布擦拭身体
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.07,0:29:26.02,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,擦拭 意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.63,0:29:30.08,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个世界 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.21,0:29:31.87,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,模特可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.67,0:29:45.09,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.15,0:29:48.18,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问 这个在哪播出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.46,0:29:54.29,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放心放心 这是推广业务的DVD 不会有人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.78,0:30:08.08,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,举行纳棺仪式 首先是用棉布擦拭往生者的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.41,0:30:14.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,净身 意味着去除这个世界的疲劳 痛苦和烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.58,0:30:20.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同时 也意味着我们做好了回到那个世界的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.83,0:30:26.62,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过去 通常用普通的水清洗身体
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.12,0:30:29.96,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在从卫生的角度考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.12,0:30:33.34,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们使用消毒水浸泡过的棉布
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.20,0:30:36.41,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.99,0:30:41.50,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,擦拭他的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.36,0:30:49.03,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个过程最重要的是对往生者的尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.46,0:30:56.38,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在擦拭中 不能让列席的亲属们\N看到往生者的皮肤 这点很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.94,0:31:11.55,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在穿完衣服后 化妆之前要进行刮脸
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.36,0:31:15.80,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特别是男性 由于肌肉收缩
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.83,0:31:20.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和皮肤干燥的关系看上去很像是胡子长长了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.27,0:31:24.69,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刮脸就更重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.75,0:31:32.90,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遗体的皮肤比我们想像的更容易受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.04,0:31:37.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用手指轻轻触碰 都有可能使皮肤受损
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.97,0:31:40.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.00,0:31:46.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要小心 谨慎地完成这个过程
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.98,0:31:49.80,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.13,0:32:00.48,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.74,0:32:02.99,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.52,0:32:08.43,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事 没事 没事 放松 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.00,0:32:16.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 回来啦  - 我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.58,0:32:25.13,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.38,0:32:27.35,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的脸 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.99,0:32:31.87,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正刮脸呢 社长突然碰了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:34.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在公司里刮脸
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.93,0:32:35.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.43,0:32:39.22,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是在家用电动剃须刀刮过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.42,0:32:43.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,社长的命令 我没办法拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.91,0:32:46.25,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事没事 破了点皮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.55,0:32:48.02,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.38,0:32:51.59,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是很怪 奇怪的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.28,0:33:02.38,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的第一个工作 突然来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.22,0:33:10.23,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问 我具体都做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.54,0:33:13.94,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.02,0:33:18.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天你看着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.20,0:33:20.48,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.76,0:33:22.76,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.17,0:33:26.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一次就碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.34,0:33:31.06,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你指什么啊 没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.47,0:33:34.87,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.42,0:33:37.35,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您不要吓唬我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.01,0:33:49.03,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 让你久等了  - 哟 辛苦了 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.61,0:33:51.50,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.80,0:33:55.38,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老太太一个人住 死两个星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.84,0:33:59.73,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情况不太好 多注意点 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.24,0:34:05.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.45,0:34:10.00,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,殡葬公司 我们的雇主
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.53,0:34:14.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.87,0:34:22.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.14,0:34:47.35,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你过来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.59,0:34:57.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过来搭把手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.93,0:35:17.67,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你抬脚
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.87,0:35:21.80,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,脚
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.15,0:35:23.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.85,0:35:32.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您不是说我看着就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.36,0:35:34.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轻点 慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.39,0:35:41.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.42,0:35:42.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.82,0:35:57.88,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.93,0:36:17.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.87,0:36:25.84,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作为你的第一次 确实有些刺激过度
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.32,0:37:01.55,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你吃什么了 怎么这么臭啊  - 没吃什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.73,0:37:03.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没闻到一股怪味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.50,0:37:05.96,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你的围巾  - 哎 你干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.32,0:37:07.53,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.82,0:37:14.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后面那穿黑西服的一直在闻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.36,0:37:19.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一站 竹下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.97,0:37:30.02,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 还开着呐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.89,0:37:51.82,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放那儿就行
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.93,0:37:59.81,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 三百元  - 哦 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.26,0:38:02.00,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毛巾一百元
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.59,0:38:42.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在还能卖上个好价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.70,0:38:44.69,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是绝对不会卖的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.02,0:38:46.64,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,行了 你走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.63,0:38:51.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我这也是为妈妈着想嘛  - 别跟我打官腔 不要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.15,0:38:55.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还没老到需要你来担心的岁数
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.63,0:38:57.94,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 小诗织
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.25,0:39:01.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好大的浴池 我还可以再来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.49,0:39:03.16,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.17,0:39:07.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了小诗织 奶奶会一直开下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.91,0:39:11.16,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是大悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.56,0:39:12.77,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,山下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.02,0:39:15.79,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么时候回来的 怎么也不告诉我一声
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.08,0:39:18.66,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃...这个...对不起 回来后各种事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.12,0:39:25.00,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 是小林家的大悟
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.50,0:39:26.82,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.12,0:39:31.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说起来年头可是不短了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.52,0:39:34.97,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像听人说你现在可是出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.64,0:39:42.99,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 拉那个什么大琴  - 大提琴 就是大号的小提琴
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.25,0:39:44.99,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦...对...对 大提琴
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.25,0:39:51.19,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位叔叔在东京拉大提琴的 可了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.33,0:39:59.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的儿子也这么有出息就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.22,0:40:02.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.32,0:40:05.73,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思 现在不方便 下次喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.04,0:40:06.88,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.40,0:40:10.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次带媳妇一块来 你结婚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.49,0:40:11.02,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.30,0:40:13.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个傻瓜不来我这还是很安静的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.45,0:40:16.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是谁生了我这个傻瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.21,0:40:19.05,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说破天 我也不会把这儿卖了的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.22,0:40:21.94,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊...有了 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.12,0:40:25.05,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开啦 开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.32,0:40:27.78,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呵呵 开啦 开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.97,0:40:57.97,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.95,0:41:02.76,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃饭吧 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.66,0:41:10.92,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是隔壁的腾井先生送给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.17,0:41:16.43,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上刚杀的 所以很新鲜 说是生吃都没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.27,0:41:29.82,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还差一点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.81,0:41:40.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.12,0:41:49.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.77,0:41:59.32,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大悟
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.11,0:42:15.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.65,0:42:36.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大悟 你到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.48,0:42:45.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 等等 不行 大悟
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.72,0:42:49.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等 这太难为情了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.76,0:42:53.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别在这 太难为情了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.77,0:43:01.06,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大悟
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.20,0:43:11.77,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.16,0:43:13.53,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.94,0:43:41.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我必须遭受的惩罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.68,0:43:47.90,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为母亲最后的时刻我没有陪伴她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.65,0:43:51.62,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来我怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.79,0:44:01.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想到这些 我突然想拉大提琴
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.01,0:44:09.58,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回忆在脑海中浮现 现在 我只想拉琴
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.49,0:44:13.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.12,0:48:59.52,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看鲑鱼哪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.64,0:49:02.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.67,0:49:10.72,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才就在那 石头边上 就那
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.58,0:49:16.01,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加油 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.62,0:49:26.43,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可悲啊 拼命游上来就是为了去死
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.80,0:49:28.92,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正是死还这么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.08,0:49:37.76,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它们想回家 回到出生地
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.07,0:50:14.68,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我吃饭去 吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.69,0:50:21.58,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,社长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.48,0:50:27.63,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您路过这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.28,0:50:30.06,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪有这么巧的事儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.81,0:50:37.25,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 是缘份吧  - 胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.86,0:50:42.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你生来就是...做这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.73,0:50:47.75,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请不要信口开河
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.77,0:51:01.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 对不起 实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.92,0:51:11.66,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生气啦 生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.23,0:51:15.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 怎么搞的 佐佐木啊  - 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.06,0:51:19.48,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.07,0:51:22.63,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过五分钟了 五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.66,0:51:24.02,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.16,0:51:29.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们不是靠死人吃饭的吗...哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.29,0:51:30.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别站着了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.53,0:51:35.27,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.74,0:54:47.14,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夫人平时爱用的口红 家里还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.17,0:55:16.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把失去的人重新唤回 赋予永恒的美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.77,0:55:22.77,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个过程 平静 细致
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.40,0:55:25.90,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.20,0:55:28.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重要的是要充满爱
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.73,0:55:32.68,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目睹每一次的生死离别
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.04,0:55:39.69,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舒缓 完美 深深地打动着我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.37,0:55:49.84,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.68,0:56:01.88,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请允许我为往生者盖棺
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.29,0:57:00.53,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.95,0:57:05.91,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我为之前的话道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.18,0:57:08.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 迟到是我们的不对
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.63,0:57:12.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个 不嫌弃的话请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.60,0:57:14.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.22,0:57:17.66,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.17,0:57:22.01,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她一生中最美的一次
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.21,0:57:28.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的 十分地感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.95,0:58:10.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.23,0:58:45.67,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.83,0:58:50.01,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.38,0:58:52.93,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.19,0:58:58.96,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 不会是  - 对 是我老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.46,0:59:03.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.23,0:59:06.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娶了这么漂亮的媳妇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.54,0:59:08.55,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪里 您过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.00,0:59:14.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好泡一泡 让身体暖和起来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.86,0:59:17.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 那我就不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.28,0:59:22.59,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.77,0:59:27.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.39,0:59:33.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 您常来这儿  - 哦 有五十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.32,0:59:38.82,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该遇到过
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.32,0:59:44.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里的水很热 但是很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.26,0:59:48.35,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汲取地下水用木火加热
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.68,0:59:51.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水质会变软
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.47,0:59:55.33,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样 泡过的皮肤爽滑不搔痒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.61,0:59:57.18,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.72,1:00:00.59,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,日本第一的澡堂子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.85,1:00:09.78,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艳子 我们走了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.39,1:00:12.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慢走 再见 明天见
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.66,1:00:19.55,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来帮您吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.81,1:00:23.33,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让客人帮忙做这些 我会遭报应的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.33,1:00:35.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全靠您一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.43,1:00:39.53,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 多年前老头子去世之后
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.72,1:00:44.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当公务员的儿子 一直劝我把这卖了盖公寓
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.65,1:00:47.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这儿要是关了 街坊邻居就不方便了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.31,1:00:50.50,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁我腿脚还动得了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.80,1:00:53.79,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪里 您还正当年哪
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.09,1:00:56.81,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要多体谅他
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.32,1:01:02.39,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大悟这孩子呢心眼好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.82,1:01:05.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事儿都一个人默默地扛着
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.42,1:01:11.57,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父母离婚那会儿 他没在他妈面前哭过一次
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.32,1:01:17.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个人在澡堂里眼泪不停地掉
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.11,1:01:22.81,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瘦小的肩膀一抖一抖的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.65,1:01:29.44,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以有的时候你要多担待他呀
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.20,1:01:41.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天水怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.42,1:01:44.93,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.41,1:01:46.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞎说
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.60,1:01:48.68,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好看 很配你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.29,1:01:58.07,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全白了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.57,1:02:00.62,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天要降温了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.83,1:02:02.53,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我来  - 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.71,1:02:05.68,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎 去哪儿喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.90,1:02:08.87,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啊 我知道个地方
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.12,1:02:12.34,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 真的 不醉不回  - 不醉不回
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.46,1:02:14.53,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不醉不回 不醉不回
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.90,1:02:16.53,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不醉不回
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.67,1:02:37.87,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好喝 好久没这么喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.31,1:02:42.77,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有点...演歌的感觉...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.98,1:02:57.47,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些都是妈妈喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.46,1:03:00.08,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是父亲的收藏
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.04,1:03:06.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对啊 这里当初是爸爸经营咖啡屋的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.14,1:03:13.23,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别再提他了 我甚至不记得他的长相了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.22,1:03:17.80,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想过再见到他吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.27,1:03:19.84,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.77,1:03:26.86,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 要是见到他了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.48,1:03:28.84,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.61,1:03:33.13,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,揍他一顿
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.51,1:04:17.48,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父亲最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.30,1:04:31.81,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我倒是觉得
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.61,1:04:39.71,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许大悟的妈妈一直都不能忘记你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.06,1:04:45.92,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.62,1:04:49.23,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不是早把这些唱片扔掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.13,1:04:54.48,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更不用说还保管得这么好
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.41,1:05:25.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,睡了吗 说吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.46,1:05:28.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你马上过来 啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.49,1:05:29.72,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在过去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.92,1:05:33.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 站前的星星宾馆 有人上吊了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.83,1:05:37.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃 社长呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.23,1:05:41.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不巧啊 社长刚刚去了别的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.66,1:05:44.16,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你一个人...行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.65,1:05:46.94,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.32,1:06:34.63,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 路上小心  - 我走啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.86,1:06:57.41,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 早上好  - 早上好 昨天晚上辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.59,1:07:02.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,警察都被你感动了 夸你能干呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.27,1:07:07.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 啊 咬紧牙关 豁出去了  - 是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.54,1:07:11.45,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.31,1:07:17.81,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 给  - 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.08,1:07:20.65,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼睛这么红啊 没睡好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.86,1:07:24.39,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喜欢上这份工作了 是不是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.07,1:07:32.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尚春小姐是怎么做上这一行的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.56,1:07:37.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.76,1:07:43.69,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,年轻时遇到一些事情 在老家待不下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.66,1:07:45.34,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪儿
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.07,1:07:47.43,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,带广啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.10,1:07:52.54,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我呢 每个工作都做不长
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.99,1:07:56.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来就到了这里的一家小酒馆
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.84,1:08:05.13,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不久 酒馆的老板娘突然中风 很快去世了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.75,1:08:10.87,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后 社长就来了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.49,1:08:17.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是我第一次看纳棺仪式
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.91,1:08:25.54,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当时就想 要是我死了 有这样的人帮我纳棺就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.77,1:08:31.54,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么说呢 觉得他是个很特别的人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.17,1:08:37.07,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 我就来了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.87,1:08:46.71,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人的命运真奇怪啊 不知在哪儿会改变
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.32,1:08:49.75,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.13,1:08:52.68,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好茶
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.68,1:09:01.24,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,山下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.29,1:09:09.19,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你的朋友  - 你好
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.27,1:09:11.61,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用跟他招呼
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.04,1:09:13.06,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.27,1:09:15.62,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们先走 我就来
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.36,1:09:25.88,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都已经传开了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.27,1:09:27.94,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,传什么
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.30,1:09:33.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做什么都行 去找个正经的活干
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.40,1:09:40.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们走 快走
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.21,1:09:56.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.12,1:10:02.44,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.70,1:10:09.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美香
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.07,1:10:16.97,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美香
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.04,1:10:21.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.03,1:10:30.73,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仪式进行时 为了不让亲属们受到刺激\N我们要特别小心
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.77,1:10:34.91,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偶尔会遇到肛门没有堵塞物的情况
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.67,1:10:38.14,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像这样把纱布卷成柱状
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.99,1:10:44.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后把它塞进肛门里
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.67,1:10:47.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,防止液体流出来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.97,1:10:54.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.60,1:11:01.46,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你翻我的抽屉了 你怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.65,1:11:06.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是偶尔去当了一回模特
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.89,1:11:09.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经调查过你公司是做什么的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.05,1:11:17.13,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.64,1:11:26.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 为什么不告诉我  - 说了你一定会反对
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.60,1:11:27.94,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是当然啦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.15,1:11:32.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么能做那种工作 你不感到羞耻吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.20,1:11:40.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么会感到羞耻 因为要碰触尸体吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.28,1:11:45.08,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是希望你找份正常的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.24,1:11:47.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正常是指什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.48,1:11:52.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家最终都会死 我会死 你也会死
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.43,1:11:57.57,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死这件事很正常 不用讲大道理
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.92,1:11:59.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马上辞职吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.08,1:12:02.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求你了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.97,1:12:14.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我以前从来没要求过你什么
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.05,1:12:21.35,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论是大悟要放弃大提琴 还是回到老家的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.75,1:12:24.72,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我都笑着答应了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.83,1:12:32.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实 心里感到悲伤
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.14,1:12:37.23,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.82,1:12:42.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.74,1:12:46.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.40,1:12:51.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次算我求你了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.54,1:12:55.55,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就听我一次行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.91,1:13:09.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是不行呢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.72,1:13:19.96,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打算把它当成你的事业吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.14,1:13:39.32,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我回娘家 等你辞了职再来接我
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.77,1:13:43.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 美香  - 不要碰我 你不干净
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.10,1:14:33.39,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不对
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.37,1:14:36.65,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.45,1:14:41.18,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我女儿不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.33,1:14:46.75,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,头发的颜色不对
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.31,1:14:49.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全都不对
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.25,1:14:51.99,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小雪是那样的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.60,1:14:56.44,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你做得不对
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.75,1:14:59.45,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全不对
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.84,1:15:03.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重新做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.90,1:15:05.50,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.92,1:15:09.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在说这些有什么用
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.05,1:15:16.27,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你平时没有好好教育她才会落到今天这个地步
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.05,1:15:22.97,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您这么说也太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.25,1:15:24.61,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.12,1:15:29.46,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没好好地教育小雪的 不也包括您吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.81,1:15:34.93,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帐东西 都怪你骑着摩托车招摇过市
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.62,1:15:38.61,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你一个人活下来不感到羞耻吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.38,1:15:41.46,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.81,1:15:43.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.98,1:15:45.00,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你听着
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.98,1:15:48.29,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小雪她
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.62,1:15:52.84,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是那么地喜欢你 可是你呢 你却害死了她
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.85,1:15:59.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你补偿得了么？ 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.57,1:16:07.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是不是想一辈子做那个人的活来赎罪啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.85,1:16:13.22,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.37,1:16:17.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.76,1:16:23.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,社长一定会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.00,1:16:28.71,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他真的很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.69,1:16:32.01,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 不至于吧  - 当然啦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.40,1:16:34.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是公司第一个正式员工
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.91,1:16:38.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,面试的时候也不是很正式啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.11,1:16:40.00,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他都是凭直觉做事的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.95,1:16:42.77,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一看到你就知道你一定行
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.16,1:16:47.67,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.59,1:16:53.78,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 辞职的话 你还是直接跟社长说吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.29,1:16:55.58,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他就在上面
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.04,1:17:24.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.58,1:17:28.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进来
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.91,1:17:45.54,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.94,1:17:52.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你老婆还没回来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.96,1:17:55.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.03,1:17:58.78,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一块儿吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.94,1:18:01.29,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我做的比你好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.09,1:18:10.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.75,1:18:17.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.37,1:18:23.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,河豚的鱼子 烤一下蘸盐吃 很香
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.64,1:18:47.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我老婆
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.16,1:18:52.63,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,九年前 得病去世了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.20,1:19:02.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夫妻俩肯定有一个会先走
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.64,1:19:05.86,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛苦的是活着的那个
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.11,1:19:17.35,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我把她打扮得漂漂亮亮的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.38,1:19:20.74,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,送走了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.03,1:19:25.62,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是我送走的第一个
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.41,1:19:33.79,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那之后我就开始做这行了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.43,1:19:38.03,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就说这个吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.59,1:19:48.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是遗体啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.31,1:19:58.57,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一种生物靠吃另一种生物生存
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.84,1:20:02.54,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然植物除外
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.94,1:20:12.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想活着就得吃东西
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.68,1:20:16.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然吃 就吃最好的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.02,1:20:37.03,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.20,1:20:38.72,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.00,1:20:42.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好吃了 真是罪孽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.36,1:21:05.54,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从东京回到山形老家快两个月了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.68,1:21:10.73,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这期间 我度过了忐忑不安的每一天
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.18,1:21:19.82,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...真的要靠这份工作生活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.95,1:21:29.34,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.22,1:21:33.18,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.71,1:22:44.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请先把头轻轻地放下
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.90,1:22:59.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留男
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.14,1:23:13.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.37,1:23:20.14,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天多谢您了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.95,1:23:28.47,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发现自己有问题后 留男经常在外面打架
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.78,1:23:32.86,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也已经很久没好好看牢他了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.87,1:23:37.54,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是今天看到他的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.74,1:23:41.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.72,1:23:50.18,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然穿成女孩样 那小子也还是我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.35,1:23:59.75,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的是 太谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.20,1:24:28.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唔 好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.00,1:24:49.55,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.15,1:24:54.27,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是罪孽
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.20,1:25:00.99,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 大提琴带来了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.85,1:25:05.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啊 拉一曲 拉一曲
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.30,1:25:07.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我来一曲
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.65,1:25:14.63,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现场演奏还是头一回听
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.75,1:25:17.06,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你曾在交响乐团工作过啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.29,1:25:19.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 不过很快就解散了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.53,1:25:23.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 什么时候学的  - 从幼儿园开始
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.45,1:25:25.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那么久啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.50,1:25:28.46,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小时候用的是儿童专用的琴
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.51,1:25:31.19,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全是被父亲强迫学的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.54,1:25:32.97,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他很有修养吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.01,1:25:35.13,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是个没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.37,1:25:39.80,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己开了个小咖啡馆 后来和店里的女招待跑了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.10,1:25:42.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是一个十足的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.32,1:25:44.55,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.77,1:25:46.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早就死了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.40,1:25:54.79,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 想听点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.20,1:26:00.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种机会很难得 最好带点圣诞节气氛的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.53,1:26:08.50,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 你们对宗教有什么忌讳吗
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.79,1:26:10.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有没有
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.36,1:26:14.29,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本公司对佛教 基督教 伊斯兰教 印度教 都不排斥
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.38,1:26:21.29,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了 为了这个圣洁的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.03,1:27:58.38,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好 这里是NK代理 承蒙您的关照
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.85,1:28:03.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天吗 丧者姓名是
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.20,1:28:06.77,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请允许我开始为往生者举行起程仪式
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.32,1:28:11.82,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 对 就这样  - 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.88,1:28:17.05,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奶奶以前说过想要穿这长统袜
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.22,1:28:19.86,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.56,1:28:30.93,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奶奶 bye-bye
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.28,1:28:33.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奶奶 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.75,1:28:46.04,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以主耶稣基督之名 为你祈祷 阿门
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.67,1:28:47.52,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿门
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.49,1:29:33.72,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,年龄不饶人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.28,1:30:56.73,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.72,1:31:59.00,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美香
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.08,1:32:05.31,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,房间打扫过吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.79,1:32:09.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 偶尔  - 骗人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.62,1:32:11.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一次都没有
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.71,1:32:14.94,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打扫过两次
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.85,1:32:19.58,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就不能算偶尔
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.29,1:32:26.71,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样 我不在不行吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.20,1:32:34.43,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有事要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.52,1:32:35.77,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.03,1:32:41.84,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们有孩子了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.83,1:32:45.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.28,1:32:49.55,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要做父亲了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.03,1:33:01.81,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 我们不能再这样混日子了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.74,1:33:09.76,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你能堂堂正正地跟孩子 说你的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.28,1:33:15.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他一定会被人嘲笑的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.74,1:33:21.25,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不需要那么多钱 一家三口开心就好
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.31,1:33:31.03,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.83,1:33:35.95,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.14,1:33:40.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎 讲请 现在就去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.12,1:33:49.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了 马上就过去
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.86,1:33:57.41,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种时候 你还去工作
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.19,1:34:03.27,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澡堂的老奶奶 刚去世了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.64,1:34:34.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我老婆美香
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.99,1:34:49.89,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搬柴火时突然倒下 就那样去了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.63,1:34:54.71,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到最后一刻还在工作
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.66,1:35:00.65,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惜澡堂子没有了 唉 真舍不得啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.80,1:38:10.19,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来请各位擦拭往生者的面颊\N请各位依次过来 送别往生者
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.80,1:38:57.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.65,1:39:30.28,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.33,1:40:41.03,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诗织
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.79,1:40:45.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟奶奶说再见
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.33,1:40:49.18,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.65,1:41:02.58,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您辛苦了奶奶
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.39,1:41:17.90,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您在这里工作
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.25,1:41:29.22,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请各们亲友双手合十送别往生者
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.95,1:41:46.18,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请允许我把棺木盖上
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.73,1:42:03.32,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.01,1:42:06.82,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.34,1:43:04.48,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能让我送母亲最后一程吗
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.04,1:43:11.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.21,1:43:23.84,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道说 人在去世前会有预感吗
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.03,1:43:32.75,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去年年底 我们俩一块儿过了平安夜
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.24,1:43:39.59,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我本来想 这么大岁数了 还过什么圣诞节啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.87,1:43:44.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是她无论如何都要过
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.14,1:43:50.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,买了块小蛋糕 把蜡烛点亮了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.30,1:43:54.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们俩一起许了愿
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.30,1:44:00.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那天 她突然说
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.11,1:44:06.19,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能不能够和她一起把澡堂办下去
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.80,1:44:13.64,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在 我想明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.19,1:44:20.07,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概 因为我火烧得好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.07,1:44:34.78,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这里呆得越久 我就越是相信
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.01,1:44:41.63,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死亡 就是一扇门啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.19,1:44:48.66,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它不意味着生命的结束
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.14,1:44:54.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是穿过它 进入另一阶段
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.02,1:45:00.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实就是门
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.13,1:45:06.61,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我呢 作为守门人
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.30,1:45:11.47,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,送很多人穿过那扇门 对他们说声
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.05,1:45:18.24,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.19,1:45:21.27,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们后会有期
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.84,1:45:24.70,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把他们送走
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.16,1:45:52.60,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.78,1:45:58.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.23,1:46:03.65,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.82,1:46:06.83,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.66,1:46:57.59,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在找什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.50,1:47:00.48,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是它了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.98,1:47:13.33,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.00,1:47:16.81,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.02,1:47:22.10,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 石头信  - 石头信
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.38,1:47:29.56,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过去 在人类还没发明文字的时代
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.71,1:47:33.61,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找一块能表达自己感受的石头 送给对方 传达信息
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.86,1:47:40.27,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿到石头的人 根据石头的手感和重量\N来揣摩对方的心意
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.58,1:47:46.07,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比如 石头很平滑就代表你很快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.42,1:47:49.79,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,粗糙凹凸就代表对方很担忧你
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.44,1:48:07.68,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.97,1:48:11.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你感受到什么了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.34,1:48:14.01,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.55,1:48:21.45,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多美的传说 谁告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.59,1:48:24.76,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.60,1:48:32.23,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那块大石头 不会就是
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.98,1:48:35.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 就是他给我的
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.89,1:48:40.97,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.18,1:48:46.97,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说每年都会给我一块 可是我只有那一块
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.11,1:48:48.77,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.34,1:49:19.44,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了小宝宝 每天都拉 直到他出生吗
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.63,1:49:38.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.07,1:49:53.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.09,1:49:57.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问这里是小林家吗
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.44,1:49:58.66,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.01,1:50:01.17,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有份小林和子的电报
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.39,1:50:07.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和子女士她不住这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.82,1:50:12.25,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 妈妈两年前就去世了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.03,1:50:17.15,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.31,1:50:19.66,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 给我看看  - 啊 不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.99,1:50:28.06,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死者姓名:小林淑希
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.19,1:50:30.80,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请来领取小林淑希的遗体
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.63,1:50:41.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我回来了 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.72,1:50:43.65,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大悟君忘带手机了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.47,1:50:47.78,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 忘家了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.92,1:50:53.77,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸去世了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.05,1:50:55.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.78,1:50:57.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.61,1:51:02.42,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.46,1:51:07.63,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我马上给吴良浜渔协打了电话才问清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.52,1:51:13.11,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说是因为爸爸的遗物里有家里的地址
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.57,1:51:17.91,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在来认我这个儿子了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.47,1:51:24.55,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都三十年没见过他了 这事该去找跟他一起私奔的那个人
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.21,1:51:28.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说他一直都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.76,1:51:35.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天一早就要火化
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.51,1:51:39.37,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说爸爸的遗体放在他们的渔夫协会了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.75,1:51:51.00,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟他们说 户口本上没他的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.84,1:51:56.02,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 所以我不能在文件上签字 拜托你了 就这样  - 大悟
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.16,1:52:02.53,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.73,1:52:04.55,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我为什么要去
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.98,1:52:06.90,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托了 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.72,1:52:17.16,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.60,1:52:22.36,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把亲生儿子扔在了带广
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.14,1:52:27.30,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他那时候六岁
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.85,1:52:32.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我喜欢上别人了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.28,1:52:37.57,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈 妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.98,1:52:39.08,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他不停地叫着
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.62,1:52:43.51,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还是甩开他的小手
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.03,1:52:47.09,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.13,1:52:58.45,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来见过他吗
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.77,1:53:04.81,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我当然想见孩子 可不行
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.54,1:53:08.63,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.35,1:53:13.16,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想看就应该去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.41,1:53:28.34,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么抛弃孩子的父母都这样
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.81,1:53:33.91,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也太不负责任了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.41,1:53:52.81,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求你了 去看看吧 去跟他作最后的道别
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.86,1:54:11.06,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大悟
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.27,1:54:53.32,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,社长
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.63,1:55:12.25,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.67,1:55:18.13,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,挑一个你喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.27,1:55:25.58,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别客气
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.72,1:55:51.58,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早晨我过来 发现已经硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.11,1:55:55.05,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.17,1:56:00.22,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也不知道他从哪儿来的 一个人跑到这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.57,1:56:02.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直拼命干活
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.20,1:56:06.14,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮了我们不少的忙
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.39,1:56:11.07,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他就住在这个门房里
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.20,1:56:13.26,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.65,1:56:20.80,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他话特别少 难得说几句
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.59,1:56:28.90,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 太好了 家人能来接他
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.11,1:56:36.85,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火葬场的人马上就该到了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.20,1:57:05.21,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是...你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.27,1:57:12.20,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说来很滑稽
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.12,1:57:16.66,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经想不起
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.56,1:57:19.91,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父亲的样子
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.38,1:57:27.84,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到他的脸 我还是想不起来
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.06,1:57:40.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小林淑希的遗物
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.94,1:57:51.92,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他这一生 到底为了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.14,1:58:00.98,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活了七十多年 只留下了一箱杂物
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.82,1:58:06.46,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.43,1:58:12.49,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 拜托了  - 对不起 打扰了 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.95,1:58:22.61,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问可以抬走了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.67,1:58:42.91,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样放里边吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.92,1:58:46.27,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 请问  - 啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.46,1:58:51.96,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- 让我自己来行吗  - 不用 不用 这事交给我们好了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.13,1:58:56.23,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等我们把他放进棺材 你给他喝点水就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.29,1:58:57.88,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一 二
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.03,1:59:03.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.79,1:59:08.81,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我丈夫是入殓师
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.40,2:04:18.76,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,2:04:23.80,2:04:25.61,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.37,2:04:44.12,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸